com.jme3.bullet.animation

Class TorsoLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme3.bullet.animation.PhysicsLink
      • com.jme3.bullet.animation.TorsoLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Savable, JmeCloneable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class TorsoLink
extends PhysicsLink
    Link the torso of an animated model to a rigid body in a ragdoll.

    This class is shared between JBullet and Native Bullet.
